article_title: WSJ Calendar of Important Dates in 2014
article_text:
Here are key dates to watch in the year ahead for big political, economic and corporate events world-wide.

* =This month

January

* U.S. Congress is expected to adopt a new five-year farm bill.

* Boeing is set to decide where to assemble its planned 777X jetliner.

* Frequent fliers on American Airlines and US Airways get reciprocal benefits on both carriers, first big step in integration.

1 Latvia joins the euro zone. Greece assumes the European presidency.
